      <guid isPermaLink="false">c3c21b9b5440f3021811018ea6db0c5d94a4dcbd</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Jul 2025 18:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a1aba2ee329058a389600c690db84a76dd53fe13.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=e63379d9832b99b0f151a67c0761a590"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5c3f1340a148b9fa0b54a824d7d1407e36aa1168.png?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=4b423cd14a3b31de839534b75a27849a"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Expand your horizons with real-world assets&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Level up your game creation with our latest asset bundle from Dekogon! Choose from a massive selection of premium-quality environments and set pieces—subways, safe houses, grocery stores, police stations, and more—with the versatile Open World Adventures Kit. Unlock game-ready assets like the &lt;em&gt;Military Training Facility&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;1996 Police Headquarters&lt;/em&gt;, and others, perfect for expanding environmental storytelling and themed level design. Add style to your next project—and help support Whale and Dolphin Conservation with your purchase!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $5 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildings_vol12_towndoorsnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Buildings VOL.12 - Town Doors (Nanite &amp; Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildingsvol13_sidewalksvertexpaintabledebriswaterdamagedirt"&gt;Buildings VOL.13 - Sidewalks (Vertex Paintable Debris/Water/Damage/Dirt)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildings_vol15_attachments"&gt;Buildings VOL.15 - Attachments&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildings_vol16_flowerbeds"&gt;Buildings VOL.16 - Flower Beds&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#decals_vol1_townsigns"&gt;Decals VOL.1 - Town Signs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#decals_vol2_roadsandstreets"&gt;Decals VOL.2 - Roads and Streets&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#decals_vol3_blood"&gt;Decals VOL.3 - Blood&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#decals_vol4_decay"&gt;Decals VOL.4 - Decay&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#decals_vol5_grunge"&gt;Decals VOL.5 - Grunge&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#foliage_vol12_grasslowpoly"&gt;Foliage VOL.12 - Grass (Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#foliage_vol18_grasslandslowpoly"&gt;Foliage VOL.18 - Grasslands (Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#quarantinemedicaltent"&gt;Quarantine Medical Tent&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#realisticmaterials_vol7_waterandice25plusmaterials"&gt;Realistic Materials Vol. 7 - Water &amp; Ice (25+ Materials)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#realisticmaterials_vol8_middleeastern30materials"&gt;Realistic Materials Vol. 8 - Middle Eastern (30 Materials)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#realisticmaterials_vol2_suburbanexterior50plusmaterials"&gt;Realistic Materials VOL.2 - Suburban Exterior (50+ Materials)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#roadcracksvollowpoly"&gt;Road Cracks VOL. (Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#scans_vol2_clothesnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Scans VOL.2 - Clothes (Nanite &amp; Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#scans_vol4_cemeterynaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Scans VOL.4 - Cemetery (Nanite &amp; Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#scans_vol5_cardboardboxesnanite"&gt;Scans VOL.5 - Cardboard Boxes (Nanite)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#scans_vol6_producenaniteplusmidpolypluslowpoly"&gt;Scans VOL.6 - Produce (Nanite + Mid Poly + Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#scans_vol7_firewoodnaniteplusmidpolypluslowpoly"&gt;Scans VOL.7 - Firewood (Nanite + Mid Poly + Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#signage_vol3_smalltownnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Signage VOL.3 - Small Town (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#signage_vol4_smalltown"&gt;Signage VOL.4 - Small Town&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#stores_vol1_shopandgrocerydisplaysnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Stores VOL.