target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="scans_vol4_cemeterynaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="scans_vol4_cemeterynaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Scans VOL.4 - Cemetery (Nanite &amp; Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/0ccc8044ea476be55b7b40482e6278781a02dbdd.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ff92ec0529508e658e1d5dc2afb3d0cc"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Scans VOL.4 – Cemetery (Nanite &amp;amp; Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Includes &lt;strong&gt;gravestones, monuments, crosses&lt;/strong&gt;, and broken or weathered headstones scanned from real-world cemetery locations. Nanite and low-poly ready for horror or urban decay scenes. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="scans_vol5_cardboardboxesnanite"&gt;&lt;a id="scans_vol5_cardboardboxesnanite"&gt;Scans VOL.5 - Cardboard Boxes (Nanite)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a06562db7dc257cf80a0ce9fe68a971430ff243d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=271d9b4bbbd9c9cd8efeba5b83db3099"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Scans VOL.5 – Cardboard Boxes (Nanite)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A set of &lt;strong&gt;highly detailed cardboard boxes&lt;/strong&gt;, including crushed, taped, open, and sealed variants. Scanned from real-world packaging—perfect for warehouses, deliveries, and clutter scenes. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="scans_vol6_producenaniteplusmidpolypluslowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="scans_vol6_producenaniteplusmidpolypluslowpoly"&gt;Scans VOL.6 - Produce (Nanite + Mid Poly + Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/11db7779af416f7bd303cff593d684aae00db036.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=cb034d869399f42e0961bba7d82f0feb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Scans VOL.6 – Produce (Nanite + Mid Poly + Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A realistic set of &lt;strong&gt;scanned fruits and vegetables&lt;/strong&gt;, including individual produce items and grouped crates. Available in Nanite, mid-poly, and low-poly versions—great for grocery scenes, kitchens, or markets. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/af2186a5-3e17-405c-b01e-8f5698d470da" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="scans_vol7_firewoodnaniteplusmidpolypluslowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="scans_vol7_firewoodnaniteplusmidpolypluslowpoly"&gt;Scans VOL.7 - Firewood (Nanite + Mid Poly + Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7e1ab2ef784cec4b9554c9d708ab52a7b9e63c18.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=dec680d13ace616a548f892174aeae37"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Scans VOL.7 – Firewood (Nanite + Mid Poly + Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A collection of &lt;strong&gt;firewood piles, chopped logs, and wood bundles&lt;/strong&gt; in multiple LODs including Nanite—perfect for campsites, cabins, survival scenes, or winter environments. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="signage_vol3_smalltownnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="signage_vol3_smalltownnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Signage VOL.3 - Small Town (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/bbec597ed4eaed69727df4900ac0c65d8366be11.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f9e36bcc2c38ebb86988b2ee174b0453"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Signage VOL.3 – Small Town (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A set of nostalgic &lt;strong&gt;small town signs&lt;/strong&gt;, including classic store boards, vintage roadside signage, and versatile low-poly and Nanite-ready props—perfect for rural or retro-themed scenes. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/b680aadf-ce9a-4497-b764-35b451e02773" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="signage_vol4_smalltown"&gt;&lt;a id="signa