&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This &lt;strong&gt;wall decor pack&lt;/strong&gt; brings suburban personality to your interiors, featuring framed photos, quirky signs, clocks, and paintings—ideal for homes, diners, and general lifestyle scenes. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/8ba1a4aa-011c-470d-9408-7e22d77b95f5" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="suburbs_vol22_shedandgardennaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="suburbs_vol22_shedandgardennaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Suburbs VOL.22 - Shed &amp; Garden (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/210a4ea54b46fb915286fcedb97a1735b4b2669c.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=12996963ff6c3f9dfafb915d47e167dc"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Suburbs VOL.22 – Shed &amp;amp; Garden (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Includes detailed &lt;strong&gt;shed and garden structures&lt;/strong&gt; with Nanite and Low Poly versions—perfect for backyards, suburban lots, or rural areas. Models include sheds, tools, buckets, hose reels, and more. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/bfdf9e3d-b47e-41f8-b173-0e9629f7f2a1" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="suburbs_vol23_gardenboxesnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="suburbs_vol23_gardenboxesnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Suburbs VOL.23 - Garden Boxes (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1ba28065fae3f187f3e4874893cdac6a531f6e75.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d145412f319419d61f17f14d7b84eeda"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Suburbs VOL.23 – Garden Boxes (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A tidy pack of &lt;strong&gt;raised garden boxes&lt;/strong&gt;, featuring planters filled with soil, flowers, vegetables, and modular variants for different layouts—great for home gardens or community lots. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="suburbs_vol24_apartmentnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="suburbs_vol24_apartmentnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Suburbs VOL.24 - Apartment (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5fe48724047cbde1f71070ad47a634add6e5298d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=90402161fbd811cd5022262929f799a4"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Suburbs VOL.24 - Apartment (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Detailed apartment interior with modular Nanite and low poly assets. Includes furniture, fixtures, and layout pieces for realistic suburban environments. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/7788e6f4-2221-4e1d-9f3e-59614b969474" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="suburbs_vol27_outdoorandyardspacesnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="suburbs_vol27_outdoorandyardspacesnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Suburbs VOL.27 - Outdoor and Yard Spaces (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/42eb0cf605b691b8de3940fc2899c7fb242d7716.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=56ae3b529db67c3aa0a3b5bbcaa412ed"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Suburbs VOL.27 - Outdoor and Yard Spaces (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Outdoor suburban yard assets including fences, patio items, grills, and landscaping props. Modular and Nanite-ready for performance. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/01dc6bc8-c44a-42ce-8ead-0c435e87ae52" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="survivorssafehouse"&gt;&lt;a id="survivorssafehouse"&gt;Survivor's Safe House&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e438cf0f909e08f29830c82fe9ed819d3df232f8.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=81a7c4e412999c5ce2fcb06a17cc3bd8"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Survivor's Safe House&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Post-apocalyptic safe house interior filled with survival gear, furniture, and environmental storytelling props. Ideal for horror and survival games. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/08505161-4ff1-48e7-9c55-b2c9515e2df2" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="trash_vol2_floordebris"&gt;&lt;a id="trash_vol2_floordebris"&gt;Trash VOL.2 - Floor Debris&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/d6b333d6b5ab36de9f8e676ac8630343b75d211b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d2cdea17b593ece4f6021e20b618dfe3"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Trash VOL.2 - Floor Debris&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Scattered floor debris set including trash piles, papers, wrappers, and clutter. Excellent for realism and scene dressing. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/53b4ae2f-b205-41df-beac-83535d428be7" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="safehouse_vol1_suppliesandgunsnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="safehouse_vol1_suppliesandgunsnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Safe House VOL.1 - Supplies and Guns (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/0ae25c5972c078c7d74e0434601555aa5f733755.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ffcbe1193f225337c344d71dd8eb98c5"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Safe House VOL.1 – Supplies and Guns (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;survivalist's safe house prop pack&lt;/strong&gt; including firearms, ammunition, storage crates, canned goods, and tactical gear. Available in both Nanite and low-poly formats—ideal for apocalyptic and shooter environments. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt15"&gt;Pay $15 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="1996policeheadquarters"&gt;&lt;a id="1996policeheadquarters"&gt;1996 Police Headquarters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ea9d68a7a499f933e0a59081352fdcede7e2dc1e.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=248ae44e7578361bb1f57b90dedccd54"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Police Headquarters Environment&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Detailed police HQ environment featuring modular walls, office desks, interrogation rooms, lockers, and tactical props. Includes realistic lighting setups and PBR textures—perfect for crime, detective, or training simulation scenes. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/ca315ca8-0bee-4e2c-846e-6995f029c797" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="boatyard_vol7_fishingnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="boatyard_vol7_fishingnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Boatyard VOL.7 - Fishing (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e23d520a197df8777782c21af89ed2b1ce918da5.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=8842851f4a88ddee9e804e62ff1482e6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Boatyard VOL.7 - Fishing (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A charming and detailed Boatyard VOL.7 - Fishing environment, designed with Nanite-optimized and low-poly geometry. Includes boats, nets, wooden docks, barrels, ropes, and marine props. Perfect for seaside, fishing-themed, or harbor scene setups. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/8c32f446-b460-402f-a315-2d0b6d8b21e8" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="churchvol1_interiorprops"&gt;&lt;a id="churchvol1_interiorprops"&gt;Church VOL.1 - Interior Props&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/8b56d7c3bd824782e794dc2ce4f7d2899897cfe8.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=3210f760a5d3d23d134b747431f982f6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Church VOL.1 – Interior Props&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A detailed collection of &lt;strong&gt;church interior props&lt;/strong&gt;, including pews, altars, chandeliers, stained glass elements, candles, lecterns, and ornamental details. Fully PBR‑textured with Nanite and low‑poly variants—ideal for sacred, historical, or atmospheric scenes. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/ece1798b-9ed1-4177-bd93-233fd844510b" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="doubletriangledinerrestaurant"&gt;&lt;a id="doubletriangledinerrestaurant"&gt;Double Triangle Diner Restaurant&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/cf50a5ad6ce65b96cdf8057d612d19fedc74d135.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e0ce011280cf196b5fe7246fa6eb80ae"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Double Triangle Diner Restaurant&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A retro-style &lt;strong&gt;diner interior&lt;/strong&gt;, complete with booths, a counter, neon signage, kitchen equipment, and vintage textures—designed for storytelling, 50s‑style visuals, or roadside stop scenes. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/370da0a1-5440-4dd4-b141-16ec1e4a5b90" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="foliage_vol16_boxwoodbushesnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="foliage_vol16_boxwoodbushesnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Foliage VOL.16 - Boxwood Bushes (Nanite &amp; Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/83a55518c100b0c883f9f260e3fae4e9d8703942.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=afb8a86ca19b088b8bc42649324da43d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Foliage VOL.16 - Boxwood Bushes (Nanite &amp;amp; Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A neat pack of &lt;strong&gt;boxwood bush foliage&lt;/strong&gt;, with trimmed spherical shrubs in Nanite-optimized and low-poly form, complete with customizable material parameters and 4K textures. Great for hedges, garden borders, or manicured landscape layouts. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/5359be1e-8258-4406-a83e-009ac6b9a9ff" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="foliage_vol22_wildgrasslowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="foliage_vol22_wildgrasslowpoly"&gt;Foliage VOL.22 - Wild Grass (Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/35e68a6d206fd9c7ca102a8957752de731b66940.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=843a1f6ff909e9fadbfb72f9654a864d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Foliage VOL.22 – Wild Grass (Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A natural &lt;strong&gt;wild grass kit&lt;/strong&gt;, with assorted low-poly grass strands, ground turf clumps, and scattered weeds—well-suited for rural or untamed landscape visualization. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/6fb9ddc0-ee5b-42d2-bfcb-dac83f402c39" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="foliage_vol23_ivylowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="foliage_vol23_ivylowpoly"&gt;Foliage VOL.23 - Ivy (Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/985e009990c5dc4f2c526a9b0a81441b5c67cca4.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=3e9d1457959d85c6036bd708ff171ef7"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Foliage VOL.23 – Ivy (Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A climbing &lt;strong&gt;ivy foliage pack&lt;/strong&gt;, including wall-bound vines, hanging tendrils, and scattered ivy leaf clusters—great for adding natural detail to architecture, ruins, or urban walls. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/ec7e450a-7488-4488-a357-651d871446a1" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="foliage_vol25_sunflowerslowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="foliage_vol25_sunflowerslowpoly"&gt;Foliage VOL.25 - Sunflowers (Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/20244f0946cb785463fa225760aab95207340ca7.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=3129d2e2218e92eaf52ab9baab4a62ec"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Foliage VOL.25 – Sunflowers (Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A sunny and vibrant &lt;strong&gt;sunflower foliage pack&lt;/strong&gt; featuring fully modeled, low‑poly sunflowers with 4K textured petals, stems, leaves, and procedural variations. Ideal for bright outdoor fields, stylized farm scenes, and nature environments. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/17e7734f-2c6e-487c-bbf1-41ca1532efbb" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="foliage_vol27_beachgrasslowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="foliage_vol27_beachgrasslowpoly"&gt;Foliage VOL.27 - Beach Grass (Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/d4c553852a80c769642e7b6600554fa228dbaca1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ec56e7ba2422d8acf6c3dc13ee2ccd24"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Foliage VOL.27 – Beach Grass (Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A breezy &lt;strong&gt;beach grass foliage pack&lt;/strong&gt; featuring low-poly grass tufts, dune plants, and coastal vegetation with realistic swaying animations. Perfect for seaside, dune, and coastal scene creation in stylized environments. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/9a3f203c-4760-47e8-afe7-d9315d39f541" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="highschoolsciencelabclassroom_90sthemeddayandnightlighting"&gt;&lt;a id="highschoolsciencelabclassroom_90sthemeddayandnightlighting" href="https://youtu.be/vCa3Wy9hS6Q"&gt;High school Science Lab Classroom - 90's themed (Day/Night Lighting)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c275e29155c4914ab93a72df3430117323fc6530.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d42c7c9e7e066fdc7c22ef84681bd399"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;High School Science Lab Classroom - 90's themed (Day/Night Lighting)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A nostalgic &lt;strong&gt;’90s-style science lab/classroom&lt;/strong&gt; complete with lab tables, glassware, chalkboards, educational posters, and dual day/night lighting setups. Perfect for educational, retro, or cinematic scenes. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="holidays_vol1_halloweendecornaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="holidays_vol1_halloweendecornaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Holidays VOL.1 - Halloween Decor (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/40e9b505b0daa79be3d9b1c477b9487bfd871936.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=16a899014c96589d2cfa00f429f319fc"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Holidays VOL.1 - Halloween Decor (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A spooky pack of &lt;strong&gt;Halloween-themed decor&lt;/strong&gt;—includes pumpkins, lanterns, cobwebs, skulls, and carved jack-o’-lanterns. Offered in both Nanite and low-poly form with PBR materials. Great for seasonal scenes or horror ambiance. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/1bdd3fdc-ecfd-4110-b4c3-fa5e35184b5d" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="holidays_vol2_halloweendecornaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="holidays_vol2_halloweendecornaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Holidays VOL.2 - Halloween Decor (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2e9113e8f98273d7433df96d0b00e220e8293e30.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c15de19b55fc952426baeda892279554"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Holidays VOL.2 - Halloween Decor (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Expand the fright with &lt;strong&gt;more Halloween decorations&lt;/strong&gt;, like graveyard props, spooky trees, tombstones, and ambient lights. Both Nanite-ready and low-poly formats included with detailed PBR textures. Ideal for haunted scenes or seasonal builds. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/6b489979-99c0-4a70-9bf5-16785d8e1c64" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="jobsite_vol1_dropclothnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="jobsite_vol1_dropclothnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Jobsite VOL.1 - Dropcloth (Nanite &amp; Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/aea0d7aebd83b1da675174fd343cdc3fe35e9239.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=07b794f7b8958a85d5f65c0a7eb94b72"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Jobsite VOL.1 - Dropcloth (Nanite &amp;amp; Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A versatile set of &lt;strong&gt;dropcloths and painter’s tarps&lt;/strong&gt;, ideal for renovation, construction, or abandoned scenes. Includes crumpled, folded, and spread-out versions with Nanite and low-poly support. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/f1cb7c2c-cf53-459c-9e81-46a1d605f1ca" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="lighting_vol5_exteriorlightsnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="lighting_vol5_exteriorlightsnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Lighting VOL.5 - Exterior Lights (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4c6f4e4c027ff11a36866a35cea118a8bfc01196.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=83e02c62409b9923ae2912fbe47e53a2"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lighting VOL.5 – Exterior Lights (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A versatile set of &lt;strong&gt;exterior lighting props&lt;/strong&gt; including lamp posts, wall sconces, industrial floodlights, and streetlights. Includes both Nanite and low poly versions for flexible use in game environments. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="realisticmaterials_vol3_suburbanexteriors50materials"&gt;&lt;a id="realisticmaterials_vol3_suburbanexteriors50materials"&gt;Realistic Materials VOL.3 - Suburban Exteriors (50 Materials)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9eba315d221a59188f33b182df9442480ddd2576.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4b1402f543ec289998d8e77f8c8bfa46"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Realistic Materials VOL.3 – Suburban Exteriors (50 Materials)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A continuation of suburban-themed PBR content with &lt;strong&gt;50 materials&lt;/strong&gt;, such as driveways, garage walls, painted trims, concrete tiles, fences, and textured siding. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="realisticmaterials_vol4_suburbaninteriors70plusmaterials"&gt;&lt;a id="realisticmaterials_vol4_suburbaninteriors70plusmaterials"&gt;Realistic Materials VOL.4 - Suburban Interiors (70+ Materials)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/0834820075300d8314fa50b7486eb188262849d7.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c91175802deffb0cdb32066b63ac65be"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Realistic Materials VOL.4 – Suburban Interiors (70+ Materials)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A curated pack of over &lt;strong&gt;70 high-quality suburban interior materials&lt;/strong&gt;, including carpets, wood floors, wallpaper, tiles, and paint—perfect for residential, cozy, or stylized home environments. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="realisticmaterials_vol6_roadsandsidewalks40plusmaterials"&gt;&lt;a id="realisticmaterials_vol6_roadsandsidewalks40plusmaterials"&gt;Realistic Materials Vol.6 - Roads &amp; Sidewalks (40+ Materials)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c066f4125b5955da76a5cae5c388cc4a256156b1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=233097ceeedacc7015771783d7527bdb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Realistic Materials VOL.6 – Roads &amp;amp; Sidewalks (40+ Materials)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This collection includes over &lt;strong&gt;40 detailed road and sidewalk materials&lt;/strong&gt;, such as asphalt, cracked pavement, concrete tiles, painted markings, and grunge overlays—great for streets and urban terrain. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/794844c7-64d4-48ce-a49a-8735223e7ae8" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="realisticmaterials_vol9_townsurfaces65plusmaterials"&gt;&lt;a id="realisticmaterials_vol9_townsurfaces65plusmaterials"&gt;Realistic Materials VOL.9 - Town Surfaces (65+ Materials)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/44f31f6a742540a9cbbd8d27c723cfdc017363d1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4dbd6108976f559493e00baaa8a059b5"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Realistic Materials VOL.9 – Town Surfaces (65+ Materials)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A large variety of &lt;strong&gt;65+ PBR materials&lt;/strong&gt; tailored for small-town environments—featuring painted wood, concrete blocks, asphalt roads, dirty brick, and more. Suitable for realistic town building surfaces. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="restaurant_vol3_diningdecornaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="restaurant_vol3_diningdecornaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Restaurant VOL.3 - Dining Decor (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/88bf808bb167b74cfd78d2b4b4c284c60f3cb96b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=b4e4b27ba69c895b824f1bc64930c026"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Restaurant VOL.3 – Dining Decor (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A stylish selection of &lt;strong&gt;restaurant dining props&lt;/strong&gt;, including modern and retro décor, tables, chairs, utensils, and place settings. Great for diners, cafés, and urban eateries. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="signage_vol5_letters"&gt;&lt;a id="signage_vol5_letters"&gt;Signage VOL.5 - Letters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/09d4488b4d7391b13d56d91d19efad8d7addef9d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=118cf5cec66a01c56df3cdac7db17a53"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Signage VOL.5 – Letters&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A modular &lt;strong&gt;3D lettering kit&lt;/strong&gt; featuring various styles of alphabet signage, marquee characters, and customizable letterforms. Ideal for creating storefront titles, neon lights, or retro signs. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="smallstructures_vol4_oceansidelowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="smallstructures_vol4_oceansidelowpoly"&gt;Small Structures VOL.4 - Oceanside [ Low Poly ]&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/cfee899876ffcd26e9bb9cb3645ab87694dc378d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0c2ab408ba934050b59593529aebb510"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Small Structures VOL.4 – Oceanside [Low Poly]&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A charming set of &lt;strong&gt;oceanside buildings and props&lt;/strong&gt;, including wooden shacks, docks, small piers, and seaside clutter—perfect for low poly coastal scenes, harbor towns, or small fishing villages. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="townbuildingsvol1_moosesdockhouse"&gt;&lt;a id="townbuildingsvol1_moosesdockhouse"&gt;Town Buildings VOL.1 - Moose's Dockhouse&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/61c92f442eadc81499217e77a5bbd517bd89b0c3.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=3b03c5943ffe4a1250e10d14d7332885"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Town Buildings VOL.1 - Moose's Dockhouse&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Highly detailed rustic dockhouse with weathered wood, signage, and fishing props. Fits perfectly in coastal town environments. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/de4b18d1-5bad-4b4c-bf70-adfb49d0dd57" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vehicles_vol10_militarylowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="vehicles_vol10_militarylowpoly"&gt;Vehicles VOL.10 - Military (Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4423eb59832fb97cf4a9ad41e2a6dce061dd87cb.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=5ddce6084d9dba856800e4c819d15b75"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Vehicles VOL.10 - Military (Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A collection of low poly military vehicles including tanks, transport trucks, and rugged utility vehicles. Game-ready and optimized. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/3cd1a69d-c8ce-455a-a253-12edb4e62ede" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vehicles_vol4_retrocarslowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="vehicles_vol4_retrocarslowpoly"&gt;Vehicles VOL.4 - Retro Cars (Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/eafdd78d668d9bc55b36920d5c79dc4ad4a2b398.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=03a784e18d55a5f4a8870349d0dc6d19"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Vehicles VOL.4 - Retro Cars (Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Low poly retro-styled cars with 70s and 80s influence. Includes sedans, hatchbacks, and wagons. Optimized and ready for open-world scenes. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/ed93c7d4-cac2-472b-9081-9cd42f73e16d" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="1970officeenvironment"&gt;&lt;a id="1970officeenvironment"&gt;1970 Office Environment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4f09b5f10c9e920fb735fbd95e6436ff5262fdf8.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=fb04bbb06aff607364d772d76468f186"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1970 Office Environment&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Recreate a slice of history with this modular 1970s military office set, complete with war-era desks, props, and paperwork. Ideal for historical games and narrative scenes. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/0750bbf8-b5d5-4cde-89fa-e275ab67ee60" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt25"&gt;Pay $25 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="ccasubwaytrainterminal"&gt;&lt;a id="ccasubwaytrainterminal" href="https://youtu.be/xNmlHWBgoPA"&gt;CCA Subway Train Terminal&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4f12b5113819ce05320ded9989df0a1f173b366b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=5a5f24180af4064d2e51f8fe92a44e04"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CCA Subway Train Terminal&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A high-detail &lt;strong&gt;subway train terminal&lt;/strong&gt; environment featuring platforms, train cars, lighting effects, and ambient details like passengers, benches, and signage. Includes Nanite-optimized geometry for seamless high-performance rendering—ideal for modern urban, sci-fi, or transit-themed scenes. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/36c54bc6-4ea5-402c-b3cc-b5094f1a8183" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="citysubwaytrainmodular"&gt;&lt;a id="citysubwaytrainmodular"&gt;City Subway Train Modular&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/872593aa4a6b7259da61c6a7639f804e43809812.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=294318d5502a9d954ae15a5b31f8006c"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;City Subway Train Modular&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A modular New York–style underground subway train environment, created for Unreal Engine with 110+ mesh assets, master materials, blueprints for lighting, floor &amp;amp; wall dirt control, graffiti decals, cinematic post-processing, and tileable textures. Ideal for urban, transit, or gritty scenes in AAA‑quality games and simulations. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/39abdcd9-baa1-49a0-bb9b-90808d483bca" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="citysubwaytunnel"&gt;&lt;a id="citysubwaytunnel"&gt;City Subway Tunnel&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7f56e20fdd051e9aaacf4d3015b510aec2a711a5.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=69d31cd0b1900ed8f710cf5ee7f2a763"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;City Subway Tunnel&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A detailed &lt;strong&gt;urban subway tunnel&lt;/strong&gt; environment featuring modular tracks, tunnel walls, lighting fixtures, cables, and ambient grime decals. Great for transit scenes, horror, or urban exploration backdrops. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/248c759c-95c3-4614-99cf-6d79dd7c9814" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="fences_vol4_oldfencesmodularnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="fences_vol4_oldfencesmodularnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Fences VOL.4 - Old Fences Modular (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/72348c925492f5ec5e7af402d853596df1d904c1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=6f1b60dfe444c283e0b4d13ef4e9f77e"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fences VOL.4 – Old Fences Modular (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A detailed modular fence kit featuring weathered wooden posts, broken panels, gate hinges, wire mesh, and overgrown moss. Includes both Nanite-optimized and low-poly variants with full PBR textures—ideal for rural environments, boundary detailing, or historical scenes. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/5d8495ea-f74b-408e-a60f-4e655ad6fd60" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="foliage_vol13_southernoaktreesnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="foliage_vol13_southernoaktreesnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Foliage VOL.13 - Southern Oak Trees (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/32bfd17f93d32bcbd6980d1d21befd46fb08cfbb.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ad64bbf3ffe1070f0d06c10abaeb4bb2"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Foliage VOL.13 - Southern Oak Trees (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A realistic &lt;strong&gt;Southern oak tree foliage pack&lt;/strong&gt;, including Nanite-optimized and low-poly variants with 4K bark and leaf textures, procedural master materials, and several size variations. Perfect for Southern forests, parklands, or landscape scenes. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/3d7ceca8-43d7-43b9-a6b2-1234145c3ef0" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="foliage_vol15_cornfieldnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="foliage_vol15_cornfieldnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Foliage VOL.15 - Corn Field (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a29c0fbfe679b32863244bc7b29ff7fad62222ce.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=06c06e859aa8510f044e2c5bb194aee6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Foliage VOL.15 - Corn Field (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A vibrant &lt;strong&gt;corn field foliage kit&lt;/strong&gt;, featuring tall stalks, leaves, tassels, and mature ear models. Includes both Nanite-ready and low-poly meshes with full texture sets—ideal for farmland, rural landscapes, or agricultural scenes. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/ba975d9e-1689-418c-bbe0-4418b9221c4f" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="foliage_vol17_groundplantslowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="foliage_vol17_groundplantslowpoly"&gt;Foliage VOL.17 - Ground Plants (Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a085666ce0e36b7d2bd894fd59de80802f9136bf.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=67fd2cca4fe5a0693c7bf1094c88b479"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Foliage VOL.17 - Ground Plants (Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A varied set of &lt;strong&gt;ground cover plants&lt;/strong&gt;, including ferns, small shrubs, leafy plants, and undergrowth—all optimized for low-poly use with stylized textures. Perfect for forest floors, garden scenes, or environment detailing. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/b0851f09-3b92-47f7-85ab-d36223c7e6aa" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="foliage_vol19_scragglybushesnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="foliage_vol19_scragglybushesnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Foliage VOL.19 - Scraggly Bushes (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6cf5da8d4b4908b31267ab7da0a18be5c3fb79ea.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=234cfc3ffa0bbd97fcf504957977145d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Foliage VOL.19 – Scraggly Bushes (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Includes a rugged mix of &lt;strong&gt;scraggly bushes&lt;/strong&gt; with both Nanite- and low-poly variants, full foliage models, exposed roots, and realistic PBR textures—great for overgrown or wild terrain environments. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/08d216aa-1c42-4564-a08c-ccf8c191d052" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="foliage_vol21_cypresstreeslowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="foliage_vol21_cypresstreeslowpoly"&gt;Foliage VOL.21 - Cypress Trees ( Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/cdf8cc3c293a0a6f93786e50a86e6eaa332cecd6.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=3484896e460045791fdf6e275c693860"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Foliage VOL.21 – Cypress Trees (Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A stately pack of &lt;strong&gt;cypress trees&lt;/strong&gt;, fully modeled in low-poly form with tall trunks, texturized branches, and dense foliage—perfect for creating pathways, groves, or stylized landscapes. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/fb78f3b5-554f-4ce3-b610-0036250e44d8" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="foliage_vol24_farmingplantslowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="foliage_vol24_farmingplantslowpoly"&gt;Foliage VOL.24 - Farming Plants (Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6223ae67fe6a7db55b772dc743dacbd136d2de57.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0fefbbba8888fea3f0807b9564bb1ce4"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Foliage VOL.24 – Farming Plants (Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A charming &lt;strong&gt;farming plant foliage pack&lt;/strong&gt; featuring modular, low-poly crops like corn, wheat, vegetables, and orchard trees. Ideal for stylized agricultural scenes in games and simulations. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/ca170b4a-a964-4ed8-83a1-d532acfe5dab" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="foliage_vol26_deadbirchtreesnanitepluslowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="foliage_vol26_deadbirchtreesnanitepluslowpoly"&gt;Foliage VOL.26 - Dead Birch Trees (Nanite + Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/55ba7d96a2bb5daf34dc59bc2ea1a366daf09aea.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=31ffc1de7e628b1e82fe99d38fe2a14d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Foliage VOL.26 – Dead Birch Trees (Nanite + Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A hauntingly beautiful &lt;strong&gt;dead birch tree foliage pack&lt;/strong&gt;, featuring both Nanite-optimized and low-poly variants. Includes detailed bark and branch textures, fallen log pieces, twigs, and ground leaf litter. Perfect for atmospheric autumn, horror, or moody forest environments. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/8f0e2b4e-e86d-450a-929c-9a20681129f5" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="foliage_vol28_ashtreesnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="foliage_vol28_ashtreesnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Foliage VOL.28 - Ash Trees (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c2e537ef726f7a7b944e9baa7acad6bd73eeecfc.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=231766a091b4c0f8faebfcc9d657ac64"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Foliage VOL.28 – Ash Trees (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A premium foliage pack featuring &lt;strong&gt;20 ash tree meshes&lt;/strong&gt; (10 Nanite, 10 low-poly) with full 4K PBR textures, master materials for surface control, and Lumen/Nanite support for Unreal Engine 5. Includes channel-packed maps, realistic bark and leaf models, ideal for forest, park, or realistic nature scenes. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/12fbf8c5-4dc4-45aa-93b3-a308da1efec2" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="foliage_vol34-yardplantsandflowerslowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="foliage_vol34-yardplantsandflowerslowpoly"&gt;Foliage VOL.34- Yard Plants and Flowers (Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/fe344e5d7ad8ba3c48e4793a122ab71265848452.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=be4e142a01d889bb359dea5a448c7248"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Foliage VOL.34 – Yard Plants and Flowers (Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A delightful &lt;strong&gt;yard plant and flower pack&lt;/strong&gt;, featuring low-poly shrubs, flowering shrubs, ornamental grasses, potted flowers, and groundcover. Perfect for garden, backyard, or front-porch scenes in stylized and low-poly game environments. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/dabd6657-d1e0-4181-8e7b-ae0d68003896" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="groceryvol3_generalgoodsnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="groceryvol3_generalgoodsnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Grocery VOL.3 - General Goods (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2c7f4c81bee1fdd52110bb12af060601373b4c58.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9c9b5bee74a68459ec619c420b056c49"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Grocery VOL.3 – General Goods (Nanite and Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A well-stocked &lt;strong&gt;grocery store interiors&lt;/strong&gt; asset pack—including shelves, canned goods, produce crates, shopping baskets, signage, and checkout counters. Fully Nanite-optimized and also available in low-poly, with PBR textures. Ideal for market scenes or retail environments. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/623bb85e-6423-40dd-83f4-2be9d0490b53" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="jobsite_vol12_officenaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="jobsite_vol12_officenaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Jobsite VOL.12 - Office (Nanite &amp; Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e455a3a519bf6f46bcbf7e4c7c11052e2ad94b45.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=73eeb1505b4e07479f41a7468d76f9ae"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Jobsite VOL.12 - Office (Nanite &amp;amp; Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A full set of &lt;strong&gt;modular jobsite office assets&lt;/strong&gt;—from desks, clipboards, and chairs to lunch boxes and scattered paperwork. Perfect for adding realism to construction trailers or temporary workspace scenes. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="jobsite_vol13_farmhaynaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="jobsite_vol13_farmhaynaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Jobsite VOL.13 - Farm Hay (Nanite &amp; Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1a851fa9ca0bf3d589555acf1d467483aa3c51c2.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9641a290dae7d8e415cd2ddf307ea131"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Jobsite VOL.13 - Farm Hay (Nanite &amp;amp; Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Includes &lt;strong&gt;modular hay bales, feed piles, and farm clutter&lt;/strong&gt; assets tailored for rural or construction-themed projects. Nanite and low-poly variants included for efficient performance. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="jobsite_vol2_modularstorageandsuppliesnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="jobsite_vol2_modularstorageandsuppliesnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Jobsite VOL.2 - Modular Storage and Supplies (Nanite &amp; Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/14f7e1054e88e0c8a920665c5352b69a7ee7275b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f5e8955c3f1e72a5c2a2f129f2b3e802"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Jobsite VOL.2 - Modular Storage and Supplies (Nanite &amp;amp; Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A comprehensive kit of &lt;strong&gt;storage units and worksite supplies&lt;/strong&gt; including modular shelving, paint buckets, toolboxes, and more. Built for efficient scene dressing with Nanite and low-poly support. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/3d67bfea-675f-45ed-a5cd-6c7e8f3d2cb0" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="jobsite_vol3_postalservicenaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="jobsite_vol3_postalservicenaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Jobsite VOL.3 - Postal Service (Nanite &amp; Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/fe3c5d5dd8ef310e63d044e8bddf2c7c7b858f39.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4653d24f5c212c328352b402633b6cb0"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Jobsite VOL.3 - Postal Service (Nanite &amp;amp; Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A modular set of &lt;strong&gt;postal service assets&lt;/strong&gt;, including mailboxes, parcel carts, post office furniture, and signage. Ideal for populating small-town or suburban environments with Nanite and low-poly support. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/0d1140d4-9ce8-4f6f-9b39-449f9a32c80d" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="jobsite_vol4_policestation"&gt;&lt;a id="jobsite_vol4_policestation"&gt;Jobsite VOL.4 - Police Station&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/0bec26c224e3648ef9ec289bc4a78f2a00f35615.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=34fec5e9d3f1568a7423500c675efc30"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Jobsite VOL.4 - Police Station&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A full &lt;strong&gt;police department kit&lt;/strong&gt;, featuring desks, holding cells, lockers, paperwork, evidence markers, and more. Great for modern urban environments or story-driven scenes. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="jobsite_vol6_moviesandrentalnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="jobsite_vol6_moviesandrentalnaniteandlowpoly"&gt;Jobsite VOL.6 - Movies &amp; Rental (Nanite &amp; Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/80c1d1c589054cc9ff7f2f906562ac5678107aa3.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=88ae85e02cc6b110d14019c5d6b927c4"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Jobsite VOL.6 - Movies &amp;amp; Rental (Nanite &amp;amp; Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This set contains assets for a &lt;strong&gt;classic movie rental shop&lt;/strong&gt;, including VHS tapes, posters, shelving, signage, and counters—perfect for nostalgic 80s or 90s settings. Includes Nanite and low-poly versions. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/ca9c72fd-adb5-485e-beb7-4a68abeda956" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="kingwashlaundromat"&gt;&lt;a id="kingwashlaundromat"&gt;King Wash Laundromat&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/00353be450451a179ef5ebdb62b375bd9989e43b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=5b0980fbf13dfb7a0e9efcac34ea30b0"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;King Wash Laundromat&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A highly detailed &lt;strong&gt;laundromat interior&lt;/strong&gt;, packed with washers, dryers, detergent displays, coin machines, and folding tables—ideal for slice-of-life scenes or urban storytelling. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/280c247f-3953-48bc-8d33-6808d8318ebf" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="militarytrainingfacility"&gt;&lt;a id="militarytrainingfacility" href="https://youtu.be/6LKvzDcLmfA"&gt;Military Training Facility&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/971e650aec2c31c1e30b3aa843b78eaff919778d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=576bc1e4a30c213829e933d2495c416e"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Military Training Facility&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A fully modular &lt;strong&gt;military training facility&lt;/strong&gt; environment with obstacle course structures, watchtowers, sandbag covers, concrete barriers, and urban warfare simulation setups. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="rocks_vol1_snowwetnessmossnanite"&gt;&lt;a id="rocks_vol1_snowwetnessmossnanite"&gt;Rocks VOL.1 - Snow, Wetness, Moss (Nanite)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/96f549c5b3df5463030f34ceaeb88eed42b315ba.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=08a07d9e49abe93032c6a37df64282c8"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Rocks VOL.1 – Snow, Wetness, Moss (Nanite)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A detailed collection of &lt;strong&gt;high-resolution Nanite rocks&lt;/strong&gt; with snow, moss, and wetness variants—great for alpine, forest, and winter scenes needing ultra-detailed organic formations. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="rocks_vol2_snowwetnessmossnanitepluslowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="rocks_vol2_snowwetnessmossnanitepluslowpoly"&gt;Rocks VOL.2 - Snow, Wetness, Moss (Nanite+Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/eada34f21c4005545efd104efc5bd481c4b80f7c.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=759218c822edd4a258386b34cd49e1ea"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Rocks VOL.2 – Snow, Wetness, Moss (Nanite+Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Includes a wide variety of &lt;strong&gt;natural rock formations&lt;/strong&gt; in both Nanite and low-poly formats—featuring snowy, mossy, and weathered textures for use in varied biomes from wilderness to tundra. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="rocks_vol3_snowwetnessmossnanitepluslowpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="rocks_vol3_snowwetnessmossnanitepluslowpoly"&gt;Rocks VOL.3 - Snow, Wetness, Moss (Nanite+Low Poly)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/329deea1da63958d01b03b6026e471c38a26a292.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=14e09f67706215e040dda325cb35d7f6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Rocks VOL.3 – Snow, Wetness, Moss (Nanite+Low Poly)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features &lt;strong&gt;layered boulders and rocky clusters&lt;/strong&gt; textured with snow, ice, moss, and water pooling—optimized with Nanite and low-poly options for maximum performance and realism. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="school_vol1_schoolinterior"&gt;&lt;a id="school_vol1_schoolinterior"&gt;School VOL.1 - School Interior&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/fbfb7745f994fa75388b6f1a4512143dbdd36eff.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=5b312874414f6821ec90e908d898c2a8"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;School VOL.1 – School Interior&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A modular &lt;strong&gt;school hallway and administrative interior&lt;/strong&gt; environment featuring lockers, tile floors, desks, signage, and doors. Ideal for academic or nostalgic American school settings. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="school_vol2_classroom"&gt;&lt;a id="school_vol2_classroom"&gt;School VOL.2 - Classroom&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3fd89ebc9a014a196b4e27455229c96a2103043a.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=025a50d5faeaf5f39f2423c0be88699b"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;School VOL.2 – Classroom&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A full &lt;strong&gt;modular classroom kit&lt;/strong&gt; with chalkboards, desks, chairs, ceiling lights, projectors, and floor tiles. Great for both old-school and modern education spaces. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/39c09820-806e-4c9a-9b4c-6686226a512e" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="school_vol3_sciencelab"&gt;&lt;a id="school_vol3_sciencelab"&gt;School VOL.3 - Science Lab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9404d95af28075657434b4dd10651e6ce85b9eb4.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=6e6fbfb0e8c607901e4696b3f4d2e2c7"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;School VOL.3 – Science Lab&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;science classroom set&lt;/strong&gt; with lab desks, stools, chalkboards, chemical props, glassware, and overhead lighting. Built for vintage or 90s-era educational themes. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="reistanceholdout"&gt;&lt;a id="reistanceholdout"&gt;Resistance Holdout&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/25e209b30256e55601ce05e9cd51c2101ab3e031.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=80570b51e7899c6e01c1fff7f4b7e368"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Resistance Holdout&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A post-crisis &lt;strong&gt;survivor hideout&lt;/strong&gt; scene, including barricades, bunks, supplies, dim lighting, and distressed structural elements—perfect for resistance bases or urban combat staging. &lt;a target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="anemoiamanor"&gt;&lt;a id="anemoiamanor"&gt;Anemoia Manor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3f60d1d0153d7aa71285519e4a4bc87d0baf75cf.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=44d7ffbb15970a4d26677a799bf1d326"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Anemoia Manor&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Immerse yourself in the &lt;strong&gt;Anemoia Manor&lt;/strong&gt;—a high-fidelity, AAA-quality haunted mansion environment created in Unreal Engine 5 with Nanite and Lumen support. Featuring 958 meshes, fully detailed textures, master-material controls, dynamic lighting scenes, and both low-poly and Nanite-friendly versions. Perfect for horror-themed, interior-driven scenes or immersive storytelling. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/5ff66818-b91e-4705-8a7a-652c771885a9" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
