      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4b90988577794879855e28c740bdbf25122b0910.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=036438c15ed696d2a777e194e8f2a5e0"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/b1b7ccdae9d90f2dc954fe0ecd77533efc1ebd4e.png?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=ef9ee93b5e63444d6d6b8a5df1c45be4"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Embark on an audio odyssey&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Want to level up the sound design on your next game or creative project? Stop wasting time and call in the heavy hitters with powerful asset packs like the &lt;em&gt;Anime Music Pack&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;Mutated Beings Sound FX Pack&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;Orchestral Ambient Music Pack&lt;/em&gt;, and more. Set sail for savings and stellar sound with the Sound Odyssey Bundle from Ovani Sound—your go-to source for crafting the perfect audioscape. Pay what you want for this ultimate audio asset collection and help support the Children's Miracle Network with your purchase!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#comedymusicpack"&gt;Comedy Music Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#electronicmusicpack_vol9"&gt;Electronic Music Pack Vol. 9&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#synthpopmusicpack_vol2"&gt;Synthpop Music Pack Vol. 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sportssoundfxpack_vol2"&gt;Sports Sound FX Pack Vol. 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bugssoundfxpack_vol2"&gt;Bugs Sound FX Pack Vol. 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#wildwestsoundfxpack"&gt;Wild West Sound FX Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt20"&gt;Pay $20 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#ambientmusicpack_vol10"&gt;Ambient Music Pack Vol. 10&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#animemusicpack_vol3"&gt;Anime Music Pack Vol. 3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#epicmusicpack_vol4"&gt;