;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Returning with Volume 3 of the Unplugged Music Pack by Ovani Sound, this collection offers raw, acoustic performances brimming with warmth and authenticity. Perfect for heartfelt scenes, nature explorations, or laid-back storytelling.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;A total of 50 music files!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;With each individual track, you’ll find three different intensity levels, each lasting approximately 90 seconds, along with a 30-second rough cut and a 60-second rough cut. Five different variants per track! With 10 distinct tracks, this diverse selection ensures seamless integration into your projects, providing the perfect musical backdrop.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Furthermore, our tracks offer even more value by seamlessly looping when used with our Music Integration Plugins, providing you with enhanced flexibility for your game development process.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;48khz/24bit&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="villainsmusicpack_vol2"&gt;&lt;a id="villainsmusicpack_vol2"&gt;Villains Music Pack Vol. 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/91fa8a6e963477e4a9e4725034b762345fdf7771.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=b5c56e2c6e004f16abc79a9d8368c246"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;iframe width="100%" height="450" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" allow="autoplay" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/playlists/2048321538%3Fsecret_token%3Ds-QJAwUKiNtvn&amp;amp;color=%23ff5500&amp;amp;auto_play=false&amp;amp;hide_related=false&amp;amp;show_comments=false&amp;amp;show_user=false&amp;amp;show_reposts=false&amp;amp;show_teaser=false&amp;amp;show_playcount=false"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Returning with Volume 2 of the Villains Music Pack by Ovani Sound, amplify your dark side with ominous themes, sinister melodies, and tension-filled arrangements. Ideal for boss fights, evil lairs, or any moment demanding musical menace.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;A total of 50 music files!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;With each individual track, you’ll find three different intensity levels, each lasting approximately 90 seconds, along with a 30-second rough cut and a 60-second rough cut. Five different variants per track! With 10 distinct tracks, this diverse selection ensures seamless integration into your projects, providing the perfect musical backdrop.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Furthermore, our tracks offer even more value by seamlessly looping when used with our Music Integration Plugins, providing you with enhanced flexibility for your game development process.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;48khz/24bit&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="jinglesandstingerssoundfxpack_vol4"&gt;&lt;a id="jinglesandstingerssoundfxpack_vol4" href="https://youtu.be/4JmLdDtoUZA"&gt;Jingles &amp; Stingers Sound FX Pack Vol. 4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5e1372a9d26b513aff754cee045dfcb5e2b8f7af.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2797b972cedad25b20a30264f4b2e617"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Introducing Jingles &amp;amp; Stingers Vol. 4 by Ovani Sound – a diverse and imaginative collection of musical cues designed to heighten feedback, flavor transitions, and signal key gameplay moments with flair.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This pack features 225 thoughtfully designed stingers, categorized for easy integration:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;• 30 Hits and One-Shots – Sudden accents and dramatic cues for impactful moments.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 30 Longs – Sustained tones perfect for ambient flourishes and audio transitions.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 38 Positives – Upbeat, rewarding stingers for success, progress, or level completion.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 38 Neutrals – Subtle cues for system actions, confirmations, or idle transitions.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 38 Negatives – Tense, unsettling effects for errors, denials, or game overs.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 20 Risers and Reverses – Directional sounds for transitions, reveals, and intensity build-ups.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 34 Shorts – Quick cues to punctuate action, toggle states, or enhance tactile feedback.&lt;p&gt;From arcade-inspired 8-bit flourishes to orchestral drama, this collection is packed with audio tools to elevate your game's audio language and polish.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;44.1kHz / 16bit&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each file includes metadata tags to reduce search time during implementation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="foley_summersoundfxpack"&gt;&lt;a id="foley_summersoundfxpack" href="https://youtu.be/sUTUI9wI3wU"&gt;Foley: Summer Sound FX Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/b504a7b0401e4e9561b24a28d90e8c558c58bd95.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=5e0be44c129510eb34f054309a107472"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Introducing the Foley: Summer Sound FX Pack by Ovani Sound – your one-stop shop for audio that captures the sizzle, splash, and leisure of summertime fun. Perfect for games set in backyards, campgrounds, beaches, or sun-soaked suburban scenes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With a total of 215 all-new sound files, this pack delivers a wide variety of seasonal Foley:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;• 32 BBQ Sounds: Lid clanks, lighter clicks, and sizzling grates set the scene for a summer cookout.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 10 Chores Sounds: Clothespins, line movements, and other breezy weekend to-dos.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 11 Heat Sounds: Oscillating fans, button clicks, and whirring motors cool things down.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 28 Hose Sounds: Water sprays, splashes, and foliage spritzes from every angle.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 15 Sleeping Bag Sounds: Zippers, whooshes, and nighttime rustling from summer camp setups.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 74 Toys Sounds: Beach balls, kites, towel whips, squirt guns, and everything else you’d expect in a backyard free-for-all.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 45 Yard Sounds: Shovels digging, garden shears clipping, and satisfying yard work Foley.&lt;p&gt;From BBQ ambiance to playful chaos, each sound is newly recorded for this pack – no recycled content.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;44.1kHz / 16bit &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Every file is tagged with metadata for quick, searchable implementation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="atompunksoundfxpack"&gt;&lt;a id="atompunksoundfxpack" href="https://youtu.be/dACNQgLnNfA"&gt;Atom Punk Sound FX Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/52ce369db7fe50f26b123d451ae8947e56cb319d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=1120bb141604bcdae025dc3d87cc15cb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Introducing the Atom Punk Sound FX Pack Vol. 1 by Ovani Sound – a retro-futuristic blend of decayed technology, mutated threats, and cold war chaos. Perfect for projects that combine mid-century nostalgia with post-apocalyptic grit.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With a total of 187 original sounds, this pack delivers iconic audio for radioactive survival, sentient machines, and 50s-era wastelands:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;• 39 Characters Sounds: Ghoulish snarls, military bots, and robot butlers full of personality and menace.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 22 Consumables Sounds: Crunchy bites, fizzy drinks, stim shots, and retro radiation cures.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 12 Environment Sounds: Reverberating bunkers, distant booms, and vault doors groaning open.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 21 Interactables Sounds: Scraps, junk, and workbench clatter echoing across the wasteland.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 19 Tools Sounds: Geiger counter ticks, power suit activations, and high-tech movement.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 61 UI Sounds: Cassette clicks, terminal hums, notification pings, and analog interface quirks.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 13 Weapons Sounds: Clunky junk guns and scrappy laser fire built from scavenged parts.&lt;p&gt;Every file is brand new and crafted for this pack – no recycled content.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;44.1kHz / 16bit &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each file is tagged with detailed metadata for quick and easy implementation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="horrorandsuspensesoundfxpack_vol4"&gt;&lt;a id="horrorandsuspensesoundfxpack_vol4" href="https://youtu.be/Xuosf9bwRtA"&gt;Horror &amp; Suspense Sound FX Pack Vol. 4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/186bae8c3239b287a010444f50984a550903a42a.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=3c0462ea5830e34321f9c184d5bfb116"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Returning with Volume 4 of the Horror &amp;amp; Suspense Sound FX Pack by Ovani Sound – an eerie evolution filled with all-new audio designed to haunt, jolt, and unnerve. These spine-chilling sounds are perfect for psychological thrillers, paranormal games, and supernatural horror.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With 178 total sounds, this pack explores the darkest corners of your imagination with atmospheric loops, grotesque creatures, and distorted ambiance.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;• 8 Ambience Loops: Clocktowers, cultist chambers, rotten swamps, and other haunting locations.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 40 Creatures Sounds: Banshees, digital husks, blight oracles, and other unspeakable horrors.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 10 Drones Sounds: Industrial decay, abyssal pressure, and whispering static to build dread.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 19 Impacts Sounds: Thuds, strikes, malfunctions, and obsidian shatters with sinister weight.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 40 Musical Sounds: Cursed pianos, liminal tones, server hums, and corrupted audio textures.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 11 Static Noise Sounds: Phantom transmissions and broken signals with haunted distortion.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 20 Tension Sounds: Massive risers and unsettling downers to elevate dramatic suspense.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 10 Whispers Sounds: Unintelligible murmurs in ancient tongues, ideal for spectral terror.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 20 Whooshes Sounds: Ghastly flutters, eerie sweeps, and dark stingers for creepy transitions.&lt;p&gt;Each sound is brand new and exclusive to Volume 4 – no recycled content.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;44.1kHz / 16bit &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each file is tagged with detailed metadata for fast implementation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bta1"&gt;Pay more than the average of $17.42 to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
