s made to look real and be easy to use. Whether it’s for a cinematic scene, an open-world game, or a slice-of-life project, this area is ready to go.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Here’s what I packed for you:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modular entertainment area structure (walls, doors, floors, ceiling lights)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Arcade machines, pool table, air hockey, pinball units&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Snack bar props: vending machines, popcorn stands, soda dispensers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Neon signs, seating, wall art, clutter props&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Interior and exterior areas with lively colors, signs of use, and cozy lighting&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Key Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;PBR textures with 2K &amp;amp; 4K resolution (Albedo, Normal, Roughness, AO, Metallic)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Nanite-compatible meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Custom collisions for gameplay-ready, Optimized for both interior and exterior lighting setups&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material instances for easy color tweaks&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Technical details&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;179 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;4096&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2048&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;1024&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Texture Size: 4096 for detailed Assets, 2048 for Mid-sized Assets, &amp;amp; 1024 for small assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Collision: Yes, Custom collisions for complex assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;LODs: Yes, 4 LODs for complex assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Number of Meshes: 179 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 149&lt;/li&gt;&lt