      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ecd9b184c41e008598e3179801661ccf4407c140.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=65a778ce3b75204b8e6491b45a58e136"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/446d4167e90f7b8660ccdb2fcdd0313efada2570.png?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=3ffb475bd5436d6635eec60d3459c3fe"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Turn up the volume with powerful assets&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Crank up the volume on your next game or creative project with The Ultimate SFX &amp; VFX Bundle. Create the perfect audio-visual vibe with this massive library of royalty-free assets—featuring 100+ sounds and effects, from realistic medieval combat clinks and clanks to spot-on gunfire and more. Pay what you want for the tools you need to dial in your project’s SFX &amp; VFX—and help support the Breast Cancer Research Foundation with your purchase!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxfruitmatchgamethemesound"&gt;SFX Fruit Match Game theme sound&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#cosmos50discountcode"&gt;Cosmos %50 Discount Code&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt5"&gt;Pay $5 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxretropolicestation"&gt;SFX Retro Police Station&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxcharacterfootsteps"&gt;SFX Character Footsteps&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt15"&gt;Pay $15 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxmedieval-combatweaponsandimpacts"&gt;SFX Medieval-Combat Weapons &amp; Impacts&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfx-medievalcharactermovement"&gt;SFX-Medieval Character Movement&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxmedievalarmorandbodyimpactpack"&gt;SFX Medieval Armor &amp; Body Impact Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#vfxexplosionunrealengine"&gt;VFX Explosion (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxcyberpunkguns"&gt;SFX Cyberpunk Guns&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#vfxdustunrealengine"&gt;VFX Dust (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxpostapodiner"&gt;SFX Post Apo Diner&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxsoulslike"&gt;SFX Soulslike&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxwarzone"&gt;SFX Warzone&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxwinter"&gt;SFX Winter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxbaristasim_coffeeshopessentials"&gt;SFX Barista Sim - Coffee Shop Essentials&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxinventory_realisticobjectinteraction"&gt;SFX Inventory - Realistic Object Interaction&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxretailcheckout_moderncoffeeshopaudiopack"&gt;SFX Retail Checkout - Modern Coffee Shop Audio Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxmedievalgore"&gt;SFX Medieval Gore&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxfootstepscrouch"&gt;SFX Footsteps Crouch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxcharacterlandings"&gt;SFX Character Landings&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxcarpack"&gt;SFX Car Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxdrone"&gt;SFX Drone&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxcyberpunkmotor"&gt;SFX Cyberpunk Motor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxsuvvehicle"&gt;SFX SUV Vehicle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sfxcyberpunk"&gt;SFX Cyberpunk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#vfxsmokeunrealengine"&gt;VFX Smoke (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#vfxbloodunrealengine"&gt;VFX Blood (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#watervfxunrealengine"&gt;Water VFX (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#cosmos1monthsubscription"&gt;Cosmos 1 month subscription&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxfruitmatchgamethemesound"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxfruitmatchgamethemesound"&gt;SFX Fruit Match Game theme sound&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/26628102ea335a8b6df0ad8c41e86a8d03dc5e0f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=552599ba762bbb3ea3104b6fa15ae141"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A lighthearted and catchy theme music pack designed for mobile games. Ideal for main menus, intro screens, and background loops in casual, puzzle, or arcade-style mobile titles.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="cosmos50discountcode"&gt;&lt;a id="cosmos50discountcode"&gt;Cosmos %50 Discount Code&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a986d343c83517a50cb2456760619802a9d37937.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9194715502a4f92d422ce7985a0f6514"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;50% Discount code valid for all Leartes Studios Products&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;https://cosmos.leartesstudios.com/&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Redemption period only valid for 3 month&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt5"&gt;Pay $5 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxretropolicestation"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxretropolicestation"&gt;SFX Retro Police Station&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f0afc6d64981e211d9a0d4bd9d0247b430e98236.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9ffb0da651c86682a3df0ae4b64b4a7a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A retro police station-themed sound pack featuring 20 immersive effects in both MP3 and WAV formats. Includes classic police car sounds, ambient loops, typewriters, swinging lamps, smoking, fan hums, ticking clocks, and police radio chatter—perfect for noir scenes, detective games, and atmospheric interiors.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxcharacterfootsteps"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxcharacterfootsteps"&gt;SFX Character Footsteps&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1710a090f4ca8f5a414dd2705c31f4b467b7004d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=65cce209cc879e209297e64512c07123"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A subtle footsteps sound pack focused on crouch walking over carpeted surfaces. Ideal for stealth gameplay, slow movement sequences, and interior infiltration scenes in immersive environments.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt15"&gt;Pay $15 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxmedieval-combatweaponsandimpacts"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxmedieval-combatweaponsandimpacts"&gt;SFX Medieval-Combat Weapons &amp; Impacts&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e03b461a3630d8cf0ee1a22ff333c86af0404ef0.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2521c06796ebb567f3163e6eed94e0f0"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A compact medieval SFX pack featuring sword equip/unequip actions, mechanical loading sounds, and realistic armor movement. Ideal for inventory, character preparation, or blacksmith scenes in fantasy or historical games.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfx-medievalcharactermovement"&gt;&lt;a id="sfx-medievalcharactermovement"&gt;SFX-Medieval Character Movement&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/16a2555930364a462c2a0e6a5ec5af3f2f9fc1f2.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=91d4a88660258891723790f8689776c6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A collection of sound effects capturing the natural movements of a medieval character. Includes footsteps on various surfaces, clothing rustles, armor clinks, and subtle body movements to bring authenticity and immersion to any medieval-themed project.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxmedievalarmorandbodyimpactpack"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxmedievalarmorandbodyimpactpack"&gt;SFX Medieval Armor &amp; Body Impact Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/b5703bff20553c6cf7ac1b63bd6e699cc215c1a8.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=55f2c01f699561061aa6dd97c0c6afa3"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A detailed collection of medieval body impact sounds, covering hits on chainmail, leather, and metal armor. Ideal for fantasy RPGs, action games, or any project needing authentic melee feedback and immersive damage effects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vfxexplosionunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="vfxexplosionunrealengine"&gt;VFX Explosion (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6752e7b51f23ae6dd3bb53aaa96eeb1f4f3411e5.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=502f5665678a96f00ba139089d5e60eb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Game-ready custom Explosions for your Unreal Engine Games&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unreal Engine Version: 5.0&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxcyberpunkguns"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxcyberpunkguns"&gt;SFX Cyberpunk Guns&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/458d98eadedb8eca80e7a6ecc56604d517c26831.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2f01f6165ecfaa2aea8a82a920e25017"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A cyberpunk-themed weapon SFX pack featuring a variety of guns including pistols, rifles, shotguns, and sniper fire. Each weapon class includes multiple variations with futuristic energy bursts, mechanical reloads, and high-tech firing sounds—ideal for sci-fi shooters and dystopian action games.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vfxdustunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="vfxdustunrealengine"&gt;VFX Dust (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/d57db8e66a2c0983120d7f787cf94ed28bc1b3ee.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=558ca8c6b2a2a9a858e174136d6a8952"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A realistic VFX pack featuring dust, ash, and dust cloud effects tailored for Unreal Engine. Perfect for explosions, collapses, and atmospheric detailing in cinematic or gameplay environments.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxpostapodiner"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxpostapodiner"&gt;SFX Post Apo Diner&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/36e6891b393260b143738f7e7777faa5fc4cf830.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=3cc7a46b5a2158def3111f0496b14058"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A themed sound pack inspired by American post-apocalyptic diners, featuring 34 immersive sound effects. Includes indoor and outdoor ambiences, bell rings, metal cabinet interactions, a looping jukebox track, and a crunchy plate break—perfect for narrative scenes, retro-futuristic settings, and moody exploration sequences.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxsoulslike"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxsoulslike"&gt;SFX Soulslike&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e18bca258ec6b939fc25daaa49e01bc973de55e4.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=3b7aaa4bbd684d3404493352766ce4d2"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A dark and atmospheric sound pack crafted for Soulslike games, featuring 26 haunting effects. Includes eerie indoor and outdoor ambiences, ancient bell tolls, bone breaks, creaking doors, and soft grass footsteps—ideal for moody exploration, cryptic storytelling, and tense encounters.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxwarzone"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxwarzone"&gt;SFX Warzone&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c9feb87c3b88f2d310e4ec1e062f78fcb565155b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=1ab6242a5d6e76542e0f6652cd816acd"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A comprehensive destruction and atmosphere-focused SFX pack featuring 95 high-quality audio files. Includes ambient loops, intense bombing and gunfire, explosive building and glass destruction, chest opens, fluttering paper, cannonballs, and vintage sounds like ringing phones, ticking clocks, and piano melodies—ideal for war scenes, dramatic narratives, or stylized destructible environments.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxwinter"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxwinter"&gt;SFX Winter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a01bbfb3ebb7e6ace59f870934675614b923fecd.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4fa2a9ea6d35a7afac726094bf471a50"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Immerse your game in a chilling winter atmosphere with this versatile sound pack. From the crunch of footsteps on fresh snow to the cozy murmur of interior winter ambience, this collection is ideal for survival games, winter exploration, and holiday-themed experiences.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Includes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Snow walk, run, jump, and land effects&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Winter interior ambient loops&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Designed for seamless layering and immersion&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Perfect For:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Survival games, winter levels, Christmas events, exploration games.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxbaristasim_coffeeshopessentials"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxbaristasim_coffeeshopessentials"&gt;SFX Barista Sim - Coffee Shop Essentials&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/b0166e29cf6551da6e37dd50b029839afed4b62c.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c533a56fb4226bc06bf0a16ad9e5c4e8"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A set of essential sound effects capturing the everyday sounds of a coffee shop environment, including coffee preparation, equipment usage, and ambient café noises.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxinventory_realisticobjectinteraction"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxinventory_realisticobjectinteraction"&gt;SFX Inventory - Realistic Object Interaction&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/bb161b7863e27ae1c2d7ef1617690630ef5f267e.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=30b4658d299ced351487d2864e878bd9"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A practical sound pack focused on realistic object interactions. Features cardboard handling, item pickup and placement, and case movements—perfect for inventory systems, crafting mechanics, and detailed object-based gameplay.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxretailcheckout_moderncoffeeshopaudiopack"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxretailcheckout_moderncoffeeshopaudiopack"&gt;SFX Retail Checkout - Modern Coffee Shop Audio Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e016506efd10a8713e9f4ccf0f59581a55d4caf2.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c07fda7b342fafa657eb6d493646ebce"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A polished audio pack built for modern coffee shops and retail gameplay. Includes cash register sounds, receipt tearing, card reader interactions, and payment cues—perfect for tycoon games, shop sims, and immersive checkout scenes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxmedievalgore"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxmedievalgore"&gt;SFX Medieval Gore&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/904f99c144ee5803e00da0eef0a2b070ce5cb75e.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f6ff1aa1387a980e46c18adec384fcff"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A brutal collection of medieval gore sound effects, featuring blood splatters, bone breaks, and visceral impacts. Ideal for dark fantasy, Soulslike combat, or any game that demands intense and realistic damage audio.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxfootstepscrouch"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxfootstepscrouch"&gt;SFX Footsteps Crouch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e861e3262d8c3c41972387a1936ec1cb7b05eacd.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=cc7b5e6d206a6ec3953f73ab807691ed"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A focused footsteps sound pack featuring detailed character movement on various surfaces. Includes running variations on carpet—ideal for stealth games, interior scenes, and precise character locomotion audio.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxcharacterlandings"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxcharacterlandings"&gt;SFX Character Landings&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c0575ce2f767601ccd5d58f042221462c9cc42cb.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=14ffd4ed0d89081ac66419736c250603"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;SFX Character Landings delivers a variety of impactful landing sounds for characters of different weights, surfaces, and intensities. Ideal for platformers, action games, and cinematic scenes that need grounded, immersive movement audio.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxcarpack"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxcarpack"&gt;SFX Car Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6e071f8be3190fe91adbe0667ee638669d3196fa.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=b17f95e56c3455de995a0d8bcffd3ffe"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;SFX Car Pack offers a diverse collection of high-quality vehicle sound effects, including engine revs, acceleration, braking, horns, and ambient driving loops. Perfect for racing games, open-world environments, and cinematic sequences needing realistic car audio.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxdrone"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxdrone"&gt;SFX Drone&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e3df77dd04993b7c34e1cd4e677cf07ffc5ea18b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=1534d1b65fd9db096a9d8d7f50c2b217"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A futuristic drone sound pack featuring movement, alert, and danger signals. Ideal for sci-fi games, surveillance systems, and high-tech enemy units.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxcyberpunkmotor"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxcyberpunkmotor"&gt;SFX Cyberpunk Motor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c351d572df1fa97663a5e135d589a423e460419c.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=68d2b858477033db83a61073fb43e2dd"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A high-tech motor sound pack designed for cyberpunk vehicles. Includes pre-drive revs and dynamic driving sounds at various speeds—ideal for futuristic bikes, hoverbikes, and sci-fi racing games.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxsuvvehicle"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxsuvvehicle"&gt;SFX SUV Vehicle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/db2e7edd739824b450bda59ce7b96a609daa5b40.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=045c0dd062da55c00ed8428d0b574fae"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A realistic SUV vehicle sound pack featuring door interactions, horn variations, and a continuous driving loop. Perfect for urban driving scenes, simulation games, and modern vehicle systems.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxcyberpunk"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxcyberpunk" href="https://youtu.be/K1bhBMdqWq0"&gt;SFX Cyberpunk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/54d5293ed9ca7376c5cb1fd91cc39acea90b0c44.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=75b889d5b7aeec7511da305f0e5a7546"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A futuristic sound pack tailored for cyberpunk environments. Includes ambient loops, electrical malfunctions, ventilator hums, and rainy dystopian city textures—perfect for sci-fi worlds, hacking sequences, or neon-lit streets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vfxsmokeunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="vfxsmokeunrealengine"&gt;VFX Smoke (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9ace05535f5b6568170dcdd06b51e66c3bc5d8ca.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=b228981cc74b69570e508f54a2b171bf"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A realistic smoke VFX pack featuring dense fog, chimney smoke, and toxic emission effects. Perfect for environmental storytelling, industrial scenes, and atmospheric layering in Unreal Engine projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vfxbloodunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="vfxbloodunrealengine"&gt;VFX Blood (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6ed8490c81ba68d79265f461b06556d9fb8b938d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=c18bde1125cfc9125a270179e4abbd0d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A realistic blood VFX pack for Unreal Engine 5.0, including splatter, gush, and impact effects. Designed for grounded combat, horror scenes, and any project that demands visceral and authentic blood visuals.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="watervfxunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="watervfxunrealengine"&gt;Water VFX (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e7e0a696568a7ec07a7a8b3bace46347c5706831.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ab4a30091a8be98f1f99265df6742a55"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A comprehensive water VFX pack for Unreal Engine featuring realistic effects such as heavy and light rain, snow, dripping water, flowing streams, waterfalls, fountains, and leaks. Ideal for dynamic weather systems, environmental storytelling, and immersive scene building.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="cosmos1monthsubscription"&gt;&lt;a id="cosmos1monthsubscription" href="https://youtu.be/-j_eFTcEuLY"&gt;Cosmos 1 month subscription&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3fbe17edd102511d37295fae694c3cf112dc3221.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=861d5e041dfa293ab5ce305f2ec423cd"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ignite Your Creativity With Our Premium 3D Assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unleash your creative potential and bring your imagination to life like never before with our extensive selection of high-quality 3D assets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unlocks the 1000+ Props&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;https://cosmos.leartesstudios.com/assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
